2026-05-15T20:26:26.6540721Z 21    <!--
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6541062Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6541237Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6541552Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6541847Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6542156Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6542444Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6542756Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6543059Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6543705Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6543982Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6544126Z 32    -->
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6544525Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6545435Z 33-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/build/intermediates/tmp/manifest/test/debug/tempFile2ProcessTestManifest16344172418916831174.xml:34:5-79
