2026-05-15T20:26:26.6835246Z 249            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6835587Z 250            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6835898Z 251            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6836218Z 252            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6836435Z 253            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6836798Z 254            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6837125Z 255            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6837430Z 256            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T20:26:26.6837745Z 257            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
